{ Openings: Systematic Approach. Dr Emanuel Lasker - opening principles or equivalent.
Middle Game - Value of pieces - looking for hanging pieces - defending own pieces - Basically we teach them materialism and how to attack things: 4 move checkmate etc.
End Game - Basic Checkmating with several pieces on the board. Q+R+R, K + Q, or R + R usually is sufficient.

Player advances to the 900 lvl after some experience is gained in threat creation. The timeline ranges from a month to six months for the knowledge to integrate. Rating follows as quickly as rated games can be played. }
 *


