1. e4 e5 { C20 King's Pawn Game } 2. Nh3 d6 3. g3 Nf6 4. f4 Nxe4 5. Ng5 { His old tricks - making threats - is still } 5... c6 { [%cal Gg5e4] } 6. Nxe4 { His playbook is still working - therefore there is no need to grow yet. } 6... Bf5 7. Ng5 Nd7 8. c3 { [%csl Gb3][%cal Gb3f7] } 8... Nc5 9. d4 Ne4 10. Qb3 d5 11. dxe5 h6 12. Nxe4 Bxe4 13. c4 Bxh1 14. cxd5 cxd5 15. Qa4+ Ke7 16. Qa3+ Ke8 17. Bb5+ Qd7 18. Bxd7+ { [%csl Ga3][%cal Gf8a3] } 18... Kxd7 19. Qa4+ Kc7 20. Qa5+ b6 21. Qa6 Bb4+ 22. Nc3 d4 23. Bd2 dxc3 24. Bxc3 Bc5 25. b4 Be7 26. Qc4+ Kd8 27. Qxf7 Rh7 28. Qg8+ Kd7 29. Qxh7 Rc8 30. Qd3+ Ke8 31. Kd2 { Black resigns. } 1-0


